snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Pre-Order Bonus Color
snippet.description:
Street Fighter 6 launches on June 2, 2023 for PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam! Warm up with the Pre-Order Bonus, which includes Outfit 1 Color 10 for Chun-Li, Jamie, Manon, Dee Jay, Juri, and Ken.

Pre-Order Now - https://streetfighter.com/6/

*The Pre-Order Bonus Content will also be added to the game at a later date after launch.
